ReverseOscillasopy-SBM/
│
├── README.md
│   → Overview of the project, usage instructions, scenarios, pedagogy
│
├── Makefile
│   → Builds the three test harnesses (A, B, C) and a combined runner
│
├── test_harness.c
│   → Deterministic test driver for all matrix-multiply implementations
│
├── src/
│   ├── matmul_broken_A.c
│   │   → Missing write to C (silent omission bug)
│   ├── matmul_broken_B.c
│   │   → Indexing/transposition bug
│   ├── matmul_broken_C.c
│   │   → Float accumulation precision-loss bug
│   └── (future: matmul_ref.c if you add it)
│
├── examples/
│   └── sample_traces.txt
│       → ASCII oscilloscope-like traces generated by your Python script
│
└── tools/
    └── tracegen.py
        → Generates logic, memory, and bug/anomaly traces
